title: (Weds Early Bird) Amy’s Daughter Making Money Renting Out Something Of Hers + PSA for Huggy Wuggy on YouTube Kids!
itunes:title: (Weds Early Bird) Amy’s Daughter Making Money Renting Out Something Of Hers + PSA for Huggy Wuggy on YouTube Kids!
description:
Amy found out her daughter is making money renting out something at school for $1 a minute. Amy didn’t know she had taken this to school and realized it after she discovered a piece of paper with $’s on it. Should she shut it down? Bobby shares a PSA for parents about a disturbing character popping up on YouTube kids.
